entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have received the access key from the administrative building.
entries.journal_entry_description: Get administrative Access to the research facility.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Speak to the Imperial Inquisitor to get access to the research facility.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: [Han Solo] The laugh is going to be on him when Vader finds out he helped the Alliance get his Blackwing virus.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Search the rooms of the facility and find the key.
entries.task03_comm_message_text: [Klex Fulgor] That looks like a low level key, but it will work to get you in. You certainly are persistent.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Return to the Inquisitor and find out what to do next.
